        "category": "class",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Even if you've never downed a tankard of ale nor indulged in a night of rowdy revelry, you appreciate the dedication to freedom from Cayden Cailean and his worshippers. After much physical practice, you've become difficult to restrain, and if you're ever @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Grabbed], you can access a little bit of the Accidental God's luck. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to your Fortitude DC when resisting an opponent's attempts to [[/act grapple]] you or Swallow you Whole. In addition, you gain the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Liberate Self] action.</p>"
        },
